# Restart Assistance after updates

When you finish editing files under `quest_assistant/` (or related launch/runtime scripts that affect the running app), **automatically restart the local dev instance** without waiting for the user to ask.

Run from the project root:

```powershell
.\scripts\restart_assistance.ps1
```

Do this at the end of the same turn where meaningful app behavior changed (voice, UI, parser, LLM, startup, etc.). Skip restart for docs-only or build-only changes unless the user is actively testing the app.

Do not ask the user to restart manually unless the restart script fails.
